    • Constructor Detail

      • ExecutionTaskFlowCompiler

        public ExecutionTaskFlowCompiler​(java.util.Collection<ExecutionOperator> startOperators,
                                 PlanImplementation planImplementation)
        Creates a new instance that enumerates a complete ExecutionPlan.
        Parameters:
        startOperators - ExecutionOperators from which the enumeration can start (should be sources).
        planImplementation - defines the ExecutionOperators to use

      • ExecutionTaskFlowCompiler

        public ExecutionTaskFlowCompiler​(java.util.Collection<ExecutionOperator> startOperators,
                                 PlanImplementation planImplementation,
                                 ExecutionPlan existingPlan,
                                 java.util.Set<Channel> openChannels,
                                 java.util.Set<ExecutionStage> executedStages)
        Creates a new instance that enumerates a partial ExecutionPlan. In fact, provides additional Channels that have already been processed, so all their producers must not be enumerated.
        Parameters:
        startOperators - ExecutionOperators from which the enumeration can start (should be sources).
        planImplementation - defines the ExecutionOperators to use
        existingPlan - ExecutionPlan that has already been executed and should be enhanced now; note that it must agree with the planImplementation
        openChannels - they, and their producers, must not be enumerated
